---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services - Points Beyond">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p>AI-optimized content strategies for the modern search landscape</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</h2>
          <p>
            When users ask ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google AI Overview a question, your content should be the answer.
            We structure and optimize your content to be cited as the authoritative source by AI systems.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI citation strategy and content structuring</li>
            <li>Question-answer format optimization</li>
            <li>Entity and knowledge graph alignment</li>
            <li>Featured snippet and AI Overview targeting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>
          <p>
            Traditional search isn't going away—it's evolving. We combine proven SEO fundamentals with
            AI-era strategies to ensure your content performs across both conventional and AI-curated results.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Technical SEO audits and implementation</li>
            <li>Keyword research with AI query analysis</li>
            <li>Content gap identification and strategy</li>
            <li>Link building and domain authority growth</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Voice AI Optimization</h2>
          <p>
            Millions use Alexa, Siri, and Google Assistant daily. Voice search requires different optimization—
            conversational queries, concise answers, and local intent. We help you capture this audience.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Conversational keyword optimization</li>
            <li>Voice search intent mapping</li>
            <li>Local voice search strategy</li>
            <li>Smart speaker skill development consulting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="13" y2="13"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="17" y2="17"/><line x1="10" x2="8" y1="9" y2="9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>High-Volume Content Production</h2>
          <p>
            Scale your content output without sacrificing quality. We use AI-assisted workflows to produce
            hundreds of pages of optimized content that maintains your brand voice and drives results.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Programmatic content strategy</li>
            <li>AI-assisted content creation workflows</li>
            <li>Quality assurance and editorial oversight</li>
            <li>Content performance tracking and optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Brand Voice Development</h2>
          <p>
            Your brand voice is your identity. We help define, document, and implement consistent messaging
            that resonates with your audience—whether they find you through search, AI, or voice assistants.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Brand voice audit and definition</li>
            <li>AI prompt engineering for brand consistency</li>
            <li>Style guide development</li>
            <li>Content team training and enablement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Analytics & Performance</h2>
          <p>
            Measure what matters in the AI era. We track not just rankings and traffic, but AI citations,
            voice search appearances, and the metrics that show your content's true reach.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI visibility tracking and reporting</li>
            <li>Voice search performance analysis</li>
            <li>Content ROI measurement</li>
            <li>Competitive intelligence and benchmarking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Let's Build Your AI Content Strategy</h2>
        <p>Every business has unique content needs. Let's explore how Points Beyond can help you thrive in the AI search era.</p>
        <a href="/points-beyond/contact/" class="cta">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #a78bfa 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .services {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .service {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: var(--color-card-hover);
  }

  .service-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .service-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem 2rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .service-content li {
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .service-content li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .services {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .service {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-content ul {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cta {
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
